headline: Is It Too Late to Consider Ralph Lauren After Its 2025 Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Ralph Lauren still offers good value after such a large run-up, or if you may be arriving late to the party, this breakdown will walk through what the current price is really baking in. The stock has climbed 3.9% over the last week, 11.4% over the last month, and an eye-catching 59.5% year to date, capping a 64.2% gain over the last year and more than tripling over 3- and 5-year periods. Those gains have come as investors reward the brand for sharpening its focus...
